HEADWORD: Self-approving
<hw>Self`-ap*prov"ing</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Approving
one's own action or character by one's own judgment.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>One <qex>self-approving</qex> hour whole years outweighs⟦br⟧
Of stupid starers and of loud huzzas.</q> <rj><qau>Pope.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Self-asserting</ent>⟦br⟧
